st","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-sin-al-ithm","tag-bad-deeds-al-sayyiat","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-hypocrisy-al-nifaq","tag-ostentation-al-riya","tag-al-quran","tag-recitation-al-tilawah","tag-reward-al-ajr","tag-sincerity-al-ikhlas","tag-worldly-life-dunya"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-a7c","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":24550,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/03\/26\/reciters-quran-never-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":38886,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Readers of Quran never enter Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf the Quran were placed in a leatherskin and then thrown into the fire, it would not burn.\u201d Al-Bayhaqi said, \u201cIt means whoever carries the Quran and recites it will never be touched by Hellfire.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40261,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/29\/listening-reciting-ayah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38886,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Reward for listening and reciting a verse","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever listens to a verse from the Book of Allah Almighty will have a multiplied reward. Whoever recites a verse will have a light on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 8494 Grade: Hasan (fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40259,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/29\/teacher-rewarded\/","url_meta":{"origin":38886,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Teacher rewarded every time a verse recited","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever teaches a verse from the Book of Allah will have its reward as it is recited.\u201d Source: H\u0323adi\u0304th Ibn Sha\u0304dha\u0304n 150 Grade: Jayyid (very good) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14235,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/16\/recite-ascend-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38886,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Recite and ascend the levels of Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt will be said to the companion of the Quran: Recite and ascend as you recited in the world! Verily, your rank is determined by the last verse you recite.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2914 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14737,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/24\/sawm-siyam-quran-intercede\/","url_meta":{"origin":38886,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Intercession: Fasting and Quran intercede for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting and the Quran will intercede for the servant on the Day of Resurrection. Fasting will say: O Lord, I prevented him from food and desires during the day, so let me intercede for him.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38170,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/08\/28\/recite-ascend-jannah-ayah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38886,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Recite and ascend in Paradise with every verse","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 28, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt will be said to the companion of the Quran when he enters Paradise: Recite and ascend! Thus, he will recite and ascend one level for each verse until he recites the last one with\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.